General.Name: Vastra Hamnens Restaurangdrift Ab
General.Description: Västra Hamnen Corporate Finance AB (publ), an independent securities company, assists companies and their owners with advice in connection with corporate transactions in Sweden and Denmark. Its activities include raising capital on and off the stock exchange; company transfers; listing and compliance monitoring, guidance, and advisory; and stock analysis of small and medium-sized listed companies. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
